[Tip 1]
text=_Some buildings, such as the farm, have a very small working area. If the building is surrounded with trees or roads, production will stop.
sec=7

[Tip 2]
text=_Keep an eye on your fishers. After fish resources are exhausted in their working area, they will stop to fish.
sec=4

[Tip 3]
text=_"Always build a ranger’s and a gamekeeper’s hut, so you will not run out of trunks or food."
sec=5
